text: We've formed several partnerships across different tracks of projects in the space. Recently, we partnered with ChainsAtlas where we deepen the chain abstraction knowledge and collaboration. We also partnered with Google, as one of their Google Cloud Partner (GCP). By leveraging Google cloud, we are forging ahead with AI capability into our blockchain. For more details on our latest partnerships, please feel free to check our X.
